OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FGerry Adams was "directly responsible
OL,7,Ffor and complicit" in the decisions
OL,8,Fmade by the Provisional IRA to
OL,9,Fdetonate bombs in England, the High
OL,10,FCourt in London has been told.
OL,12,FJohn Clark, a victim of the 1973 Old
OL,13,FBailey bombing in London, Jonathan
OL,14,FGanesh, a 1996 London Docklands
OL,15,Fbombing victim, and Barry Laycock, a
OL,16,Fvictim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,17,Fcentre bombing in Manchester, all
OL,18,Fallege that Mr Adams was a leading
OL,19,Fmember of the Provisional IRA on those
OL,20,Fdates, including of its Army Council.
OL,26,@nD@QOUoD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/11
