OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FThe three men are bringing legal
OL,7,Faction against the former Sinn Fein
OL,8,Fpresident and are seeking #1 in
OL,9,Fdamages.
OL,11,FMr Adams denies that he had any role
OL,12,Fin the Provisional IRA and is opposing
OL,13,Fthe claim.
OL,15,FOn Monday he arrived at the Royal
OL,16,FCourts of Justice wearing what
OL,17,Fappeared to be a bullet-proof vest,
OL,18,Fand was driven into the car park.
OL,26,@oD@arr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FThe court was told that the three men
OL,7,Fwant to show how Mr Adams was involved
OL,8,Fin the Provisional IRA "in the course
OL,9,Fof that conflict and to show on the
OL,10,Fbalance of probabilities that he was
OL,11,Fas involved as the people who planted
OL,12,Fand detonated those bombs".
OL,14,FOpening her case on Monday, Anne Studd
OL,15,FKC, representing the men, also said Mr
OL,16,FAdams was "directly responsible for
OL,17,Fand complicit in those decisions made
OL,18,Fby that organisation to detonate bombs
OL,19,Fon the British mainland in 1973 and
OL,20,F1996".
OL,26,@pD@XOUtD@ZO]xD@KOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FIn written submissions, Ms Studd said:
OL,7,F"The defendant carefully draws a
OL,8,Fdistinction between being a member of
OL,9,F'the Army' and being a member of Sinn
OL,10,FFein.
OL,12,F"In reality, the evidence will
OL,13,Fdemonstrate that this was not the
OL,14,Fclear either/or choice as the
OL,15,Fdefendant would have you believe.
OL,17,F"For many individuals, we say,
OL,18,Fincluding Mr Adams, that was a
OL,19,Fdistinction without a difference."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@BrrtD@AOUyD@AOU{D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FMs Studd told the court that a
OL,7,F"jigsaw" of evidence from those who
OL,8,Fknew Mr Adams and those who knew of
OL,9,Fhim will prove the case against him.
OL,11,FShe added: "The claimants' case is
OL,12,Fthat none of these bombings in the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom mainland took place
OL,14,Fwithout the knowledge and agreement of
OL,15,Fthe defendant in his role in the
OL,16,FProvisional IRA and latterly as a
OL,17,Fmember of the seven-man Army Council."
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@HO]sD@LOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FShe concluded: "There is no doubt that
OL,7,Fthe defendant contributed to the peace
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland, but the claimants
OL,9,Fsay that on the evidence he also
OL,10,Fcontributed to the war."
OL,12,FMs Studd also told the court that Mr
OL,13,FAdams had "a foot in each camp" of the
OL,14,Fmilitary and political sides of the
OL,15,FIrish republican movement.
OL,17,FShe said: "What we have here are
OL,18,Fwitnesses who give evidence about
OL,19,Fintelligence that they saw amassed
OL,20,Fover years.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@XO]uD@KOUuD@_O]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,F"It provided details of the structure
OL,7,Fof the Provisional IRA, the election
OL,8,Fof the army executive and the
OL,9,Fappointment of those executive members
OL,10,Fof the seven-person Army Council.
OL,12,F"The Army Council set the strategy for
OL,13,Fthe Provisional IRA through all the
OL,14,Fyears of the Troubles. It did not
OL,15,Freally change in its basic
OL,16,Finformation, which was that the
OL,17,Fdefendant was an instrumental force in
OL,18,Fthe organisation of the Provisional
OL,19,FIRA and building of the two-strand
OL,20,Fattack ` Armalite and the ballot box."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU|D@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
