FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FLawyers for Mr Adams, who denies the
OL,7,Fclaims, said Mr Adams "played an
OL,8,Finstrumental role in the peace process
OL,9,Fwhich culminated in the signing of the
OL,10,FGood Friday Agreement in April 1998,
OL,11,Fwhich brought an end to the decades-
OL,12,Flong conflict".
OL,26,@oD@WOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
