OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FIn written submissions, Edward Craven
OL,7,FKC, representing Mr Adams, said: "The
OL,8,Fdefendant's alleged factual and legal
OL,9,Fresponsibility for the claimants'
OL,10,Finjuries is strongly contested, as is
OL,11,Fthe claimants' ability to bring these
OL,12,Fclaims against the defendant several
OL,13,Fdecades after the expiry of the
OL,14,Fapplicable limitation period."
OL,16,FHe added that there is "no legal or
OL,17,Fpractical reason why these claims
OL,18,Fcould not have been issued long before
OL,19,F2022".
OL,26,@oD@bOUvD@^O]xD@XOU{D@EO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,FMr Craven continued: "Even if the
OL,7,Fclaim were not bound to fail on
OL,8,Flimitation grounds, the claim must
OL,9,Finevitably fail on the merits.
OL,11,F"The defendant strenuously denies any
OL,12,Finvolvement in the bombings."
OL,14,FHe also said: "The defendant has never
OL,15,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of, still
OL,16,Fless charged or convicted of, any
OL,17,Foffence in connection with any of the
OL,18,Fbombings.
OL,26,@nD@VOUsD@AOUtD@]O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/11
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1773151902
OL,3,CGerry Adams 'responsible and
OL,4,Ccomplicit' for IRA bombings
OL,6,F"Had law enforcement authorities been
OL,7,Fin possession of information which
OL,8,Fcreated a reasonable suspicion that
OL,9,Fthe defendant may have been involved
OL,10,Fin those bombings, he would have been
OL,11,Farrested and questioned."
OL,13,FThe trial before Mr Justice Swift is
OL,14,Fexpected to end next week.
